snippet.textDisplay: it was a comic book... stop hating? it's not a bad show. Riverdale on the other hand is all over the place. But Katy Keene is all about friendship and dreams and FASHION. Don't judge so harshly (in an annoying kinda pathetic way) when literally there have only been 4 episodes out. Damn. And if you dont like it, dont watch it maybe? No one is forcing you to. I grew up on these comics and i can agree river dale became a mess. Katy Keene is actually quite cute and good in comparison. Katy Keene kinda feels like a mix of the bold type and ugly betty with tiny hints of sex and the city.
